<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <title>Welcome to GhostVault</title>
  <style>
    :root {
      /* GhostVault Design System - Dark Theme with Glassmorphism */
      --bg: #0f1724; /* deep navy */
      --panel: #111827; /* almost black */
      --muted: #9aa4b2;
      --surface: #0b1220;
      --accent: #22c1c3; /* ghost teal */
      --accent-2: #7dd3fc; /* light cyan for highlights */
      --success: #28c76f;
      --danger: #ff6b6b;
      --glass: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.03);
      --radius: 12px;
      --gap: 14px;
      font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif;
      color-scheme: dark;
    }

    * {
      box-sizing: border-box;
      transition: border-color 0.2s ease, background-color 0.2s ease;
    }

    body {
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      min-height: 100vh;
      background: linear-gradient(180deg, var(--bg), #071123);
      color: #e6eef3;
    }
    
    .container {
      background: linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.02), rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.01));
      border-radius: 16px;
      box-shadow: 0 8px 30px rgba(2, 6, 23, 0.7);
      border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);
      padding: 40px 32px;
      max-width: 480px;
      width: 90%;
      margin: 24px auto;
      text-align: center;
    }
    
    /* Header with logo */
    .header {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 16px;
      margin-bottom: 24px;
      justify-content: center;
    }
    
    .logo {
      width: 64px;
      height: 64px;
      border-radius: 16px;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--accent), var(--accent-2));
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      font-weight: 700;
      color: #031018;
      font-size: 24px;
    }
    
    h1 {
      color: #e6eef3;
      font-size: 2rem;
      margin: 0;
      font-weight: 700;
    }
    
    .subtitle {
      color: var(--accent-2);
      font-size: 16px;
      margin-bottom: 24px;
      font-weight: 500;
    }
    
    .features {
      background: linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.01), rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.015));
      border-radius: var(--radius);
      padding: 20px;
      margin: 24px 0;
      border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.03);
      text-align: left;
    }
    
    .features ul {
      list-style: none;
      padding: 0;
      margin: 0;
    }
    
    .features li {
      margin-bottom: 16px;
      padding: 12px 0;
      border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);
      font-size: 15px;
      line-height: 1.5;
    }
    
    .features li:last-child {
      border-bottom: none;
    }
    
    .features strong {
      color: var(--accent-2);
      font-weight: 600;
    }
    
    ul {
      text-align: left;
      margin: 18px 0 24px 0;
      padding-left: 20px;
    }
    
    li {
      margin-bottom: 10px;
      font-size: 1rem;
    }
    
    .get-started {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--accent), var(--accent-2));
      color: #031018;
      border: none;
      border-radius: 10px;
      padding: 14px 32px;
      font-size: 16px;
      font-weight: 700;
      cursor: pointer;
      margin-top: 24px;
      transition: all 0.2s ease;
    }
    
    .get-started:focus, .get-started:hover {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--accent-2), var(--accent));
      transform: translateY(-2px);
      box-shadow: 0 6px 20px rgba(34, 193, 195, 0.3);
      outline: 2px solid var(--accent);
      outline-offset: 2px;
    }
    
    .tip {
      background: linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.01), rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.015));
      color: var(--accent-2);
      border-radius: var(--radius);
      padding: 16px 20px;
      margin-bottom: 24px;
      font-size: 16px;
      border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.03);
      box-shadow: 0 4px 12px rgba(34, 193, 195, 0.04);
    }
    
    .aria-desc {
      position: absolute;
      left: -9999px;
      top: auto;
      width: 1px;
      height: 1px;
      overflow: hidden;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container" role="main" aria-labelledby="welcome-title">
    <div class="header">
      <div class="logo">GV</div>
      <h1 id="welcome-title">Welcome to GhostVault!</h1>
    </div>
    
    <div class="subtitle">Your secure, privacy-first password manager for the browser.</div>
    
    <div class="features">
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Pin GhostVault:</strong> Click the puzzle icon <span aria-label="Extensions">🧩</span> in your browser bar, then pin <strong>GhostVault</strong> for easy access.</li>
        <li><strong>Set your master password:</strong> The first time you save a login, you'll be prompted to set a master password. <span aria-label="Help" title="This password protects all your saved logins. Don't forget it!">❓</span></li>
        <li><strong>Save logins easily:</strong> Just log in to any website. GhostVault will offer to save your credentials securely.</li>
        <li><strong>Autofill logins:</strong> When you revisit a site, GhostVault can autofill your credentials for you.</li>
        <li><strong>Manage settings:</strong> Click the <span aria-label="Settings">⚙️</span> icon in the popup to customize your experience.</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
    
    <button class="get-started" id="getStartedBtn" aria-label="Get started with GhostVault">Get Started</button>
    
    <div class="aria-desc" id="aria-desc">After clicking Get Started, you can open GhostVault from the browser toolbar.</div>
    <script src="welcome.js"></script>
  </div>
</body>
</html> 